    <item>
      <title>英伟达股价暴跌，交易员在“真空”中关注 100 美元股价水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/nvidia-rout-has-traders-watching-100-share-level-amid-vacuum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 的市值遭遇大幅抛售，蒸发了创纪录的 2,790 亿美元。交易员们纷纷研究图表，寻找线索，以了解这种痛苦何时结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/nvidia-rout-has-traders-watching-100-share-level-amid-vacuum</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:24:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LME 力争提高月度价格，打破 147 年历史</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所（London Metal Exchange）正计划采取措施，促进其月度合约的电子交易，此举可能会减少其独特的三个月滚动合约的活动，该合约是全球金属行业的基准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
